			 described in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:6501/ss:e/p:1/sp:A/cl:i">clause (i)</cato:entity-ref> or <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:6501/ss:e/p:1/sp:A/cl:ii">(ii) of section 6501(e)(1)(A)</cato:entity-ref>
            </quote> and inserting
			 <quote>which is in excess of 25 percent of the amount of gross income stated in
			 its return</quote>.</text>
